title: EU Commission Intends to Block Amazon's iRobot Acquisition
description: European Union’s competition watchdog intends is weighing Amazon’s $1.7 billion bid to purchase Roomba maker iRobot.

title: Amazon Logistics Executive John Felton to Become AWS CFO
description: Amazon.com logistics executive John Felton is taking over as chief financial officer of the company’s cloud division, Amazon Web Services, according to people familiar with the matter.

title: Chip Giant TSMC Foresees Delay at Second Arizona Plant
description: The announcement offers further evidence that the $40 billion Arizona project is running into challenges in meeting aggressive timeline targets.

title: Children on Instagram and Facebook Were Frequent Targets of Sexual Harassment, State Says
description: A 2021 Meta Platforms presentation estimated 100,000 child users were harassed daily, according to unredacted portions of a New Mexico lawsuit.
